title: The BUA of the IH tenements constructed under the scheme shall not be counted towards FSI and such built up area shall be allowed over & above the permissible BUA under these regulations
clause_text: The BUA of the IH tenements constructed under the scheme shall not be counted towards FSI and such built up area shall be allowed over & above the permissible BUA under these regulations.
